<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Styled Page Example</title>
  <style>
    /* Style the body */
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    /* Style the header */
    header {
      background-color: #4CAF50; /* green background */
      padding: 20px;
    }

    /* Style the nav */
    nav {
      background-color: #333333;
      padding: 10px;
    }

    /* Style the main */
    main {
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      font-size: 18px;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    /* Style the footer */
    footer {
      background-color: #222222;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    /* Style the list items */
    li {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 100px;
      color: white;
    }

    /* Style the h1 */
    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
      color: #0055AA;
    }

    /* Style the paragraph */
    p {
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>Welcome to My Website</h1>
  </header>

  <nav>
    <ul>
      <li>Home</li>
      <li>About</li>
      <li>Contact</li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <main>
    <p>This is a sample paragraph to demonstrate styling. The font size and background are set using CSS.</p>
    <p>Make sure to check the color contrast using a validator like <a href="https://wave.webaim.org/">WAVE</a>.</p>
  </main>

  <footer>
    &copy; 2025 My Website
  </footer>

</body>
</html>

